apter 31 (§ 1361 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1361"},"text":"section 1361 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Endangered Species Act of 1973, referred to in subsec. (c), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/205"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–205","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-12-28"},"text":"Dec. 28, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/884"},"text":"87 Stat. 884","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 35 (§ 1531 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1531"},"text":"section 1531 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Migratory Bird Treaty Act, referred to in subsec. (c), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1918-07-03/ch128"},"text":"act July 3, 1918, ch. 128","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/755"},"text":"40 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to subchapter II (§ 703 et seq.) of chapter 7 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s710"},"text":"section 710 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
